Use Application SandboxingWhy: Isolates applications to prevent them from affecting the rest of the system.Ubuntu:Install Firejail:sudo apt install firejailRun Application in a Sandbox:firejail firefoxWindows:Use Windows Sandbox:Enable Windows Sandbox:dism /online /Enable-Feature /FeatureName:"Containers-DisposableClientVM" /AllLaunch Windows Sandbox from the Start menu and run applications in an isolated environment.
